### Environment Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api/v1
@phone = +919876543210
@otp = 123456

### ----------------------------------------------------
### 1. Authentication Module
### ----------------------------------------------------

### Send OTP
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/send-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "phone": "{{phone}}"
}

### Verify OTP (User) -> Will register if new
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/verify-otp/user
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "phone": "{{phone}}",
    "otp": "{{otp}}",
    "name": "Deven User",
    "city": "Mumbai"
}

### Verify OTP (Artist) -> Will register if new
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/verify-otp/artist
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "phone": "+919999999999",
    "otp": "{{otp}}",
    "name": "Pandit Sharma",
    "category": "Sundarkand",
    "city": "Delhi"
}

### Admin Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/admin-login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "admin@shobhnam.com",
    "password": "adminpassword"
}

### ----------------------------------------------------
### 2. User Module (Requires User Token)
### ----------------------------------------------------

### Get User Profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer <USER_ACCESS_TOKEN>

### Update User Profile
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Authorization: Bearer <USER_ACCESS_TOKEN>
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "city": "Navi Mumbai"
}

### ----------------------------------------------------
### 3. Artist Module
### ----------------------------------------------------

### List Artists (Public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/artists?page=1&limit=10&city=Delhi

### Get Artist Profile (Artist Token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/artists/me
Authorization: Bearer <ARTIST_ACCESS_TOKEN>

### Update Artist Profile (Artist Token)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/artists/me
Authorization: Bearer <ARTIST_ACCESS_TOKEN>
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "bio": "Experienced Sundarkand pathi",
    "basePrice": 2500,
    "isAvailable": true
}

### Approve Artist (Admin Token)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/artists/<ARTIST_ID>/approval
Authorization: Bearer <ADMIN_ACCESS_TOKEN>
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "status": "APPROVED"
}

### ----------------------------------------------------
### 4. Booking Module
### ----------------------------------------------------

### Create Booking (User Token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/bookings/request
Authorization: Bearer <USER_ACCESS_TOKEN>
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "artistId": "<ARTIST_ID>",
    "date": "2026-03-10T10:00:00Z",
    "type": "Sundarkand",
    "expectedAudienceSize": 50,
    "address": "123 Bhakti Road",
    "city": "Mumbai",
    "pinCode": "400001"
}

### Respond to Booking (Artist Token)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/bookings/<BOOKING_ID>/respond
Authorization: Bearer <ARTIST_ACCESS_TOKEN>
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "status": "CONFIRMED"
}

### User Bookings (User Token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/bookings/user
Authorization: Bearer <USER_ACCESS_TOKEN>

### ----------------------------------------------------
### 5. Review Module
### ----------------------------------------------------

### Submit Review (User Token) - Requires Booking = COMPLETED
POST {{baseUrl}}/reviews
Authorization: Bearer <USER_ACCESS_TOKEN>
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "bookingId": "<BOOKING_ID>",
    "rating": 5,
    "comment": "Incredible performance, highly recommended!"
}

### Get Artist Reviews (Public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/reviews/artist/<ARTIST_ID>

### ----------------------------------------------------
### 6. Admin Module (Requires Admin Token)
### ----------------------------------------------------

### Get Dashboard Stats
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer <ADMIN_ACCESS_TOKEN>

### Create Category
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/categories
Authorization: Bearer <ADMIN_ACCESS_TOKEN>
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Mata Ki Chowki",
    "description": "Devotional night for Goddess Durga"
}

### Get Categories (Public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/categories
